<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Charitable" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Charitable,</orth> full of charity, benevolent, ready or fit to relieve distress: <cit><quote>c. deeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 908" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 908</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>let him have all c. preparation,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.222" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 222</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a c. duty,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 5.107" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 107</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with c. hand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 133</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>born under a c. star,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.205" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 205</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a c. office,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.3.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 3, 80</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a just and c. war,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 36</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>license,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.74" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 74</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>deeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.35" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 35</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>care,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 67</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>murderer,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 178</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>deed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 3.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 70</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>wish,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 43</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>title,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 94</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>men,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 3.2.82" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 82</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>intents,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.4.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 4, 4